{"tid":2086161,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國安法首名入罪競猜遊戲","createTime":"2020-06-30T07:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T12:41:04.000Z","uid":241255,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1e069bee886e96bee0c3c2165267342c8c9a0c28","tid":2086161,"uid":241255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"我估河童<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142d7095ff424446a02d1ce465db0c6c08ae4e21","tid":2086161,"uid":267730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:49:49.000Z","msg":"我估連尼住"},{"pid":"56ed10ce5519e9bb9771da94c17032047ea0861e","tid":2086161,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"Jimmy Lai<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Thanks, Pompeo</span></span></strong>比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2FwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=48ca08c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地、美國廢架制裁無用（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"cf5003a7098f1f2a02cb24f85bf51bd924b329d3","tid":2086161,"uid":234392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:50:09.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎"},{"pid":"ebc9908fdcad4ddc21f7117407a47898e79d68ff","tid":2086161,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:51:17.000Z","msg":"計個官判定畀人拉？"},{"pid":"b567b141748820c5a2fb290ddd77887575da8e86","tid":2086161,"uid":241255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:52:21.000Z","msg":"究竟邊個咁好彩可以做到第一個國安法烈士？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3def0b502bc4bd2de7955c495ad9b9833dd852b9","tid":2086161,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"可能係柒婆，先捉咗佢，全面直接行事"},{"pid":"a98790ada766191c824cf4c23fff5e315b6cc902","tid":2086161,"uid":241255,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebc9908fdcad4ddc21f7117407a47898e79d68ff","tid":2086161,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:51:17.000Z","msg":"計個官判定畀人拉？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:53:08.000Z","msg":"入罪就梗係計個官判啦"},{"pid":"6d5ea3c874366374fb77bc9324d5587ea227d657","tid":2086161,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:53:13.000Z","msg":"香港好快會出現難民"},{"pid":"b2a787547fa21e24bb12bd9318660ed1fc60f5f4","tid":2086161,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:53:21.0